        <li style="color: #333;">According to a survey, blogs influence the purchasing decisions of over 60% of online
            consumers.</li>
        <li style="color: #333;">The most popular blogging platform is WordPress, powering millions of blogs
            worldwide.</li>
        <li style="color: #333;">Several renowned authors, journalists, and influencers started their careers as
            bloggers.</li>
        <li style="color: #333;">Blogs can cover a wide range of topics, including fashion, technology, travel,
            lifestyle, finance, and more.</li>
    </ul>
